name: Nambona890's Texture Edits
description: I decided to upload some useful texture edits that I made in Photoshop, that I've used in some of my WADs. They're pretty much mostly just metal and techbase texture edits, though. They're also in a ZDoom format, so you might have to do a bit of cleanup if you're using the textures for a vanilla/Boom-compatible WAD.
